    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK999">
<l>nakalvalla rallārkku māyiru ñālam</l>
<l>pakalumpāṟ paṭṭaṉ ṟiruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who cannot rejoice, the wide world is buried darkness even in (broad) day light.</l>
            </lg>
